From: rramakax <rohitx.kant@intel.com>
Date: Fri, 14 Aug 2020 16:03:58 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Fix for CtsTelephonyTestcases.

CTS telephone test cases are failing.
Disable the ril flag to disable telephony feature
to pass the telephony test cases.

Change-Id: Id96e2ad543f0012b87dbaaa912e1057328f749d5
Tracked-On: OAM-91766
Signed-off-by: rramakax <rohitx.kant@intel.com>

diff --git a/groups/telephony/default b/groups/telephony/default
new file mode 120000
index 0000000..02e4a84
--- /dev/null
+++ b/groups/telephony/default
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+false
\ No newline at end of file
diff --git a/groups/telephony/doc.spec b/groups/telephony/doc.spec
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..dbddfa8
--- /dev/null
+++ b/groups/telephony/doc.spec
@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@
+=== Overview
+
+this group is used for disabling ril.
+
+==== Options
+
+--- true
+empty dir.
+
+--- false
+this will disable the ril related property value
+
+--- default
+when not explicitly selected in mixin spec file, the default option will be used.
diff --git a/groups/telephony/false/init.rc b/groups/telephony/false/init.rc
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..9216804
--- /dev/null
+++ b/groups/telephony/false/init.rc
@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@
+on boot
+    # Disable rild
+    setprop ro.radio.noril yes
diff --git a/groups/telephony/true/empty_dir b/groups/telephony/true/empty_dir
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..e69de29
-- 
